DomainAutoApproval - ChangeLog
==============================

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Fatal error: Call to undefined function client_mail_add_default_accounts() - iMSCP 1.5.x
    Renamed: 'user_accounts' parameter to 'client_accounts'
    Renamed: 'ignored_domain' parameter to 'ignored_domain_aliases'

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Update for i-MSCP 1.3.x Serie

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Plugin must not act if the logged-in user is not the real client (See changes in i-MSCP v1.2.12 - #IP-1486)
    Fixed: Could not add domain alias with version 1.3.0
    Review: CS fixes

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Removed: Support for i-MSCP 1.1.x serie
    Renamed: disallowed_domain parameter to ignored_domain

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Updated: License headers

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Default email accounts for domain alias are not created
    Fixed: Plugin must only act at customer level

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: 'disallowed_domains' configuration parameter which allow to set a list of disallowed domains
    Changed: 'domains' configuration parameter has been renamed to 'user_accounts'
    Fixed: Plugin is broken (Entities status are now hard-coded in i-MSCP)
    Updated: License (plugin is now released under the LGPL v2.1 license)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Updated: Whole code to fit with the new plugin API version (0.2.4)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.8
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Updated: Whole code to fit with the new plugin API version (0.2.0)
    Updated: License header

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.7
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: CS fixes

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: i-MSCP compatibility version check

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Changed: Default value for approval rule is now set to FALSE in configuration file
    Fixed: #843: Bug - Plugin - DomainAutoApproval: Configuration variable `ITEM_ADD_STATUS` is missing

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: 'approval_rule' configuration parameter

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Improved: Whole code by removing useless queries

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Domain aliases are not automatically approved

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Release: First released version (through github)
